header.intro
  .intro-body
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          h1.brand-heading Web Developer
          p.intro-text Experienced with modern tools and workflow in web development.
          a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll(href="#about")
            i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated

//- About Section
section#about.container.content-section.text-center
  .row
    .col-lg-12
      h2 About Me
      hr.star-light
      p
        | I am Taufiqur Rohman, i work at Kafila International Islamic School (
        a(href="http://www.kafila.or.id") www.kafila.or.id
        | ), i teach computer with practical method, and focused on resulting a product, to help students  build their skills.
      p
        | I developed my own web based e-learning system for the school using 
        a(href="http://www.laravel.com") Laravel PHP Framework
        | , it serves students many lessons with video tutorials, quizzes and games. My other project is a web based application for Quran examination, it store scores for student memorization of quran in every pages with multiple criteria.
      p.text-center
        a.btn.btn-lg.btn-outline(href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/taufiqurrohman")
          span.fa-stack.text-primary
            i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            i.fa.fa-linkedin.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
          | Me on LinkedIn

//- Portfolio section
section#portfolio.content-section.text-center
  .portfolio-section
    .container
      .col-lg-12
        h2 Portfolio
        hr.star-primary
      .row
        .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
          a.portfolio-link(data-target="#portfolioModal1", data-toggle="modal")
            .caption
              .caption-content
                i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-3x
            img.img-responsive(src="assets/img/kafila.png", alt="")
        .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
